     I                                        1   20HH
     I                                        3   40SS
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 KEY1
     I                                        1   2 WKAT1
     I                                        3   3 HI
     I                                        4   7 WKAT2
      *
     C           Q4SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     GOTO @END
